Media Queries:
In order to incorprate multiple styles in the same css file, the @media query must be placed below the default stlying. 

*****Example:*******

This DOES works: 

.column.one-fourth {
	width: 21.25%;
}

@media all and (max-width: 640px) {
	.column.one-fourth {
		margin: 0;
		width: 100%;
	}
}

This  DOES NOT work:
@media all and (max-width: 640px) {
	.column.one-fourth {
		margin: 0;
		width: 100%;
	}
}
.column.one-fourth {
	width: 21.25%;
}
